       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COM00110.

      ******************************************************************
      *                       ERP VIA                                  *
      ******************************************************************
      * OBJECTIVO: ROTINA STANDARD DE VALIDACAO DE DADOS DE PROJECTO   *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
      *SPECIAL-NAMES.
      *    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.

      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                       PIC  X(40)
            VALUE 'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE DO COM00110      '.
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME               PIC X(10) VALUE 'COM00110'.
           05 CON-DATA-MIN              PIC X(10) VALUE '0001-01-01'.
           05 CON-4                     PIC X(01) VALUE '4'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-FACTOR           PIC S9(15)V9(05) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-ZCUNICO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CUTILIZA         PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-EMPRESAS         PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO      PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY COCK0001.
           COPY COCK0002.
           COPY VIAK0001.
           COPY VIAK0002.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIACK001.
           COPY VIAW0005.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                      PIC X(40)
            VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COM00110       '.

      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY ETCL0002.
           COPY COCL0011.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                COCL0011-COMMAREA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************

           INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE ZEROS  TO COCL0011-GMORADA-S
             MOVE SPACES TO COCL0011-GMORADA-CAPLIC
             MOVE ZEROS  TO COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG

             MOVE ZEROS  TO COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-S
             MOVE SPACES TO COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-CAPLIC
             MOVE ZEROS  TO COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1100-OBT-FAM-CONT
                 THRU 1100-OBT-FAM-CONT-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1100-OBT-FAM-CONT.
      ******************************************************************

      * Chamada aos parágrafos de informaçăo para a obtençăo
      * de familia de contacto.

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1100-OBT-FAM-CONT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1100-OBT-FAM-CONT-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCL0011-CFAMCON = COCK0002-CFAMCON-CLIENTE AND
                COCL0011-CTIPCON = COCK0002-TIPCON-MANAGER
                PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI
                   THRU 2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCL0011-CFAMCON = COCK0002-CFAMCON-CLIENTE AND
                COCL0011-CTIPCON = COCK0002-TIPCON-GERAL
                PERFORM 2200-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-GER
                   THRU 2200-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-GER-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCL0011-CFAMCON = COCK0002-CFAMCON-CLIENTE AND
                COCL0011-CTIPCON = COCK0002-CFAMCON-PROJECTO
                PERFORM 2300-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PROJ
                   THRU 2300-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PROJ-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCL0011-CFAMCON = COCK0002-CFAMCON-PESSOAS AND
                COCL0011-CTIPCON = COCK0002-TIPCON-PESSOAS
                PERFORM 2400-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PESS
                   THRU 2400-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PESS-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCL0011-GEMAILPROF = SPACES
             SET ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
             SET COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-1 TO TRUE
             MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-CAPLIC
             MOVE COCK0001-EMAIL-PROF-N-EXIST TO
                  COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-EXIT'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-IND-ERROS'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2100-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2200-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-GER.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-VALIDAR-VIA-CLI-GER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCL0011-GMORADA = SPACES OR
              COCL0011-CCODPOS = SPACES OR
              COCL0011-GLOCPOS = SPACES OR
              COCL0011-CPAIS   = SPACES
              SET ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
              SET COCL0011-GMORADA-1 TO TRUE
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCL0011-GMORADA-CAPLIC
              MOVE COCK0001-MORADA-INVALIDA TO COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG
           END-IF.

       2200-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-GER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2300-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PROJ.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PROJ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCL0011-GMORADA  = SPACES
             SET ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
             SET COCL0011-GMORADA-1 TO TRUE
             MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCL0011-GMORADA-CAPLIC
             MOVE COCK0001-MORADA-INVALIDA TO COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG
           END-IF.

       2300-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PROJ-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       2400-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PESS.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2400-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PESS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCL0011-GMORADA    = SPACES OR
              COCL0011-GTELEFONE1 = SPACES
             SET ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
             SET COCL0011-GMORADA-1 TO TRUE
             MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCL0011-GMORADA-CAPLIC
             MOVE COCK0001-MORADA-INVALIDA TO COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG
           END-IF.

       2400-VALIDA-VIA-CLI-PESS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-IND-ERROS'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE COCL0011-GEMAILPROF-MSG   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE COCL0011-GMORADA-MSG      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
            EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
      *                       AREA DE PROCEDURES                       *
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0099 END-EXEC.
           COPY VIAP0015.

      ******************************************************************
